item.title: CVE-2019-7097|2024-08-04T20:38:33.157Z -- adobe -- adobe%20dreamweaver
item.description: Adobe Dreamweaver versions 19.0 and earlier have an insecure protocol implementation vulnerability. Successful exploitation could lead to sensitive data disclosure if smb request is subject to a relay attack.
